Carol Thurston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carol_Thurston 0 Carol Thurston (September 27, 1920 – December 31, 1969) was an American film and television actress who played the fictitious Emma Clanton in eight episodes (1959-1961) of the ABC/Desilu western television series The Life and Legend of Wyatt Earp, starring Hugh O'Brian as frontier peace officer Wyatt Earp.
